{
  "stem": "13258.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I found that, upon my return to Poland, by coincidence, that there is a Jewish committee in the city of.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Katowice.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And without going into the details, I got there and finally, I found out that in that committee after-- which was not the best organized at the time because people were amateurs.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't know how to do things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were trying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody-- everybody, wherever you were during that war, Jews, very fast, were able to organize committees to help.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they had to learn some of the things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I found out that my mother and my sister had survived at a labor camp in the district of Lower Silesia, not far from [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Breslau ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the camp was known as Peterswaldau, and it was a branch of the notorious Gross-Rosen concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That was an exclusively women's camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Not far away was a men's camp in Langenbielau which had the nickname [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My mother and sister worked in a metal factory there, a factory which was making bomb mechanisms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Except for the last couple weeks before the end of the war, they were chased out to dig trenches.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But that's where they survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They subsequently came to America.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father died in February of 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He died of a bad combination of pneumonia, under-nourishment, and heartache.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was alone, he got sick, he was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't-- I had been writing to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I had also-- when we came to the Polish army we were-- to the Polish Division-- we were told that there is, in Moscow, a committee which is called the committee of Polish Patriots, which was instrumental in creating, that second time.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Polish army.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
